    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous with its care, so you won\u2019t find a single scratch or hiccup anywhere. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and feels practically brand new. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in top-tier shape, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 46500.0,
