    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its deep, mirror-like factory finish with absolutely zero rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and matte\u2014exactly as it felt on the showroom floor\u2014with the original grain perfectly preserved and that distinct new-car aroma still present. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the undercarriage remains remarkably clean, showing no signs of inclement weather use. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive binder documenting every scheduled service interval performed exclusively by master technicians. This is a museum-grade example featuring flawless glass, pristine alloy wheels with no curb rash, and an interior free of even the slightest wear on the touchpoints. For the discerning collector who demands perfection in every stitch and bolt, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical secondary market offering. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, characterized by an unblemished exterior and an interior that retains its original integrity. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been rigorously preserved, ensuring that this automobile meets the requirements of the most exacting collector. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of peerless quality and uncompromising presence.",
